verbose_text: Our results are consistent with a reported biphasic effect of GnRH agonists on growth where GnRH agonists at high doses (1 muM) inhibit cell proliferation in vitro, and cells treated with agonists at low dose (10 nM) show a significant increase in proliferation.
evidence: GnRH agonists at high doses (1 muM) inhibit cell proliferation
